title: 188: No Such Thing As A Mouth-Propelled Grenade Launcher
content: Live from Newcastle, Dan, James, Anna and Andy discuss Mo Farah's only Guinness World Record, what's inside a Kit Kat, and how hamsters arrived in the UK.
